<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="id">
  <head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8" />
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
    <title>Verifikasi OTP</title>
  </head>

  <style>
    body {
      font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
      background-color: #f4f4f9;
      margin: 0;
      padding: 0;
      display: flex;
      justify-content: center;
      align-items: center;
      min-height: 100vh;
      color: #333;
      text-align: center;
    }

    .container {
      background-color: #fff;
      padding: 20px;
      border-radius: 10px;
      box-shadow: 0 4px 10px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
      width: 100%;
      max-width: 600px;
      margin: 2rem auto;
      box-sizing: border-box;
      max-height: 90vh;
      overflow-y: auto;
    }

    .header {
      background-color: #FE4F34;
      padding: 10px;
      border-radius: 8px 8px 0 0;
      color: #fff;
      margin: -20px -20px 15px;
    }

    h1 {
      font-size: 22px;
      margin: 0;
    }

    p {
      font-size: 14px;
      line-height: 1.5;
      margin: 8px 0;
      color: #555;
    }

    .otp-code {
      font-size: 28px;
      font-weight: bold;
      color: #FE4F34;
      background-color: #f9f9f9;
      padding: 8px 15px;
      border-radius: 8px;
      display: inline-block;
      margin: 15px 0;
    }

    .button {
      display: inline-block;
      background-color: #FE4F34;
      color: #fff;
      padding: 8px 15px;
      font-size: 14px;
      font-weight: bold;
      border: none;
      border-radius: 5px;
      text-decoration: none;
      margin: 12px 0;
      cursor: pointer;
    }

    .button:hover {
      background-color: #FE4F34;
    }

    footer {
      font-size: 12px;
      color: #777;
      margin-top: 15px;
    }

    .footer-link {
      color: #FE4F34;
      text-decoration: none;
    }

    .footer-link:hover {
      text-decoration: underline;
    }

  </style>
  
  <body>
    <div class="container">
      <div class="header">
        <h1>Verifikasi OTP</h1>
      </div>
      <p>Halo {{name}},</p>
      <p>
        Terima kasih telah menggunakan layanan kami! Untuk melanjutkan permintaan Anda, harap gunakan kode OTP di bawah ini. Kode ini berlaku selama <strong>5 menit</strong>.
      </p>
      <div class="otp-code">{{otp}}</div>
      <p>Jika Anda tidak meminta kode ini, harap abaikan email ini.</p>
      <footer>
        Butuh bantuan? Hubungi kami di
        <a href="mailto:tmesra008@gmail.com" class="footer-link">tmesra008@gmail.com</a>
      </footer>
    </div>
  </body>
</html>
